## Quick Reference

### iOS (SwiftUI + Liquid Glass)
- Use `.glassEffect(.regular)` for navigation/controls
- Use `GlassEffectContainer` for related glass elements
- Never stack glass on glass
- Use spring animations with reduce motion check

### Android (Jetpack Compose + Material 3)
- Use `MaterialTheme.colorScheme` roles
- Check SDK >= 31 for dynamic color
- Use `LazyColumn` with stable keys
- Use `remember` and `StateFlow` correctly

### Cross-Platform
- 48dp (Android) / 44pt (iOS) minimum touch targets
- Test with TalkBack AND VoiceOver
- Provide button alternatives for gestures
- Respect prefers-reduced-motion

